data.description: In a very eye catching location, this corner lot house will make you feel right at home. This 3 bedroom property is ideal for everyone. Very well maintained ranch  with a new roof, and 2 car detached garage.Furnace  acquired in the last 5 years along with a new thermostat. Beautiful hardwood floors in the family room and bedrooms. Nice size yard with a storage shed. Close to parks, schools, shopping and access to 1-294 make this property a must see! Make an appointment today and enjoy the showing..
